MCQMCIntegration
================
Library to calculate Monte-Carlo and Quasi Monte-Carlo Integration.

REQUIREMENT
===========
* C++11 or C++14

INSTALL
=======

    ./configure --prefix=YOUR_INSTALL_DIR
    make
    make install

PREPARE
=======
set LIBRARY_PATH and CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH properly.

DOCUMENT
========
see [doc/index.html](./doc/index.html)



